Remove ~/.cabal and ~/.ghc
Do a `cabal update`
Update cabal: `cabal install -j cabal-install`
Update happy and alex: `cabal install -j happy alex`
Install tools: `cabal install -j hare hdevtools hlint ghc-mod hoogle stylish-haskell hindent hasktags present`
Emacs: haskell-mode company-ghc ghc hindent flycheck-haskell flycheck-hdevtools hi2 hindent
